item.description: As Newcastle United’s exciting season continues on the field, Tyne Time have teamed up with Dean ‘Midas’ Maynard, one the worlds most renowned psychics who has many successes to date. Dean and myself have agreed to have a little challenge to see who’s predictions are most accurate for the remaining 13 Coca Cola Championship games. Obviously a lot of people will be skeptic of Dean’s abilities and I must say I’m not really a man into this kind of stuff but nevertheless, it interests me.
